},[[
step
kill Portal Keeper Hasabel##124393
|tip To earn this achievement, you will need to open the Chaotic Rift.
|tip When starting the fight, do not damage the boss. Just do the mechanics.
|tip Assign one player to run in the Fire portal and pick up a fire orb. This player will then need to bring the orb into the Green portal and drop it.
|tip Assign another player to go into the Shadow portal and get shadow debuff. This player will need to bring the Shadow debuff into the Green portal, pick up the Red orb that should be in there, and then also obtain the Green debuff.
|tip Once a player has all 3 debuffs, the Chaotic Rift will open.
|tip After opening the Chaotic Rift, begin killing the boss.
|tip The Chaotic Rift will constantly pull all players toward it for the duration of the fight.
|tip The Chaotic Rift will also choose random players and place one of three debuffs on them: Fire, Fel, or Shadow.
|tip Players with these debuffs must run into the portal of the color debuff they have.
|tip So players with the Fire debuff must run into the Fire (Red) portal, players with the Fel debuff must run into the Fel (Green) portal, and players with the Shadow debuff must run into the Shadow (Purple) portal.
Earn the _Portal Combat_ achievement |achieve 11928 |goto Antorus/3 43.5,51.1
step
Congratulations!
